---
// src/components/FaqAccordion.astro
---

<section class="py-12 md:py-16 lg:py-20">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-medium text-center text-primary mb-8">
            Frequently Asked Questions
        </h2>
        <div class="space-y-4">
            <details
                class="group bg-card rounded-2xl border border-gray-100 dark:border-gray-800 shadow-lg shadow-black/5 dark:shadow-none transition duration-300 ease-in-out hover:border-brand-accent/50 hover:shadow-brand-glow"
            >
                <summary
                    class="flex justify-between items-center cursor-pointer list-none p-6"
                >
                    <span class="font-medium text-primary"
                        >What is LatteArtist?</span
                    >
                    <span
                        class="text-secondary group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform duration-200"
                    >
                        <svg
                            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                            class="h-5 w-5"
                            viewBox="0 0 20 20"
                            fill="currentColor"
                            aria-hidden="true"
                        >
                            <path
                                fill-rule="evenodd"
                                d="M5.293 7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0L10 10.586l3.293-3.293a1 1 0 111.414 1.414l-4 4a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 010-1.414z"
                                clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                        </svg>
                    </span>
                </summary>
                <div class="px-6 pb-6">
                    <p class="mt-3 text-secondary">
                        LatteArtist is an app designed for coffee enthusiasts
                        and aspiring baristas to document, track, and review
                        their latte art progress.
                    </p>
                    <p class="mt-3 text-secondary">
                        The app aims to provide a simple yet effective tool for
                        users to log their attempts, note key variables, rate
                        their satisfaction, and visually observe their journey
                        and improvement over time.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </details>

            <details
                class="group bg-card rounded-2xl border border-gray-100 dark:border-gray-800 shadow-lg shadow-black/5 dark:shadow-none transition duration-300 ease-in-out hover:border-brand-accent/50 hover:shadow-brand-glow"
            >
                <summary
                    class="flex justify-between items-center cursor-pointer list-none p-6"
                >
                    <span class="font-medium text-primary"
                        >When will the app be available?</span
                    >
                    <span
                        class="text-secondary group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform duration-200"
                    >
                        <svg
                            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                            class="h-5 w-5"
                            viewBox="0 0 20 20"
                            fill="currentColor"
                            aria-hidden="true"
                        >
                            <path
                                fill-rule="evenodd"
                                d="M5.293 7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0L10 10.586l3.293-3.293a1 1 0 111.414 1.414l-4 4a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 010-1.414z"
                                clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                        </svg>
                    </span>
                </summary>
                <div class="px-6 pb-6">
                    <p class="mt-3 text-secondary">
                        The app is currently in private beta. Signing up for
                        early access gives you access to the TestFlight beta, so
                        you can be part of a select group of early testers and
                        help shape the app.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </details>

            <details
                class="group bg-card rounded-2xl border border-gray-100 dark:border-gray-800 shadow-lg shadow-black/5 dark:shadow-none transition duration-300 ease-in-out hover:border-brand-accent/50 hover:shadow-brand-glow"
            >
                <summary
                    class="flex justify-between items-center cursor-pointer list-none p-6"
                >
                    <span class="font-medium text-primary"
                        >Is there an Android version planned?</span
                    >
                    <span
                        class="text-secondary group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform duration-200"
                    >
                        <svg
                            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                            class="h-5 w-5"
                            viewBox="0 0 20 20"
                            fill="currentColor"
                            aria-hidden="true"
                        >
                            <path
                                fill-rule="evenodd"
                                d="M5.293 7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0L10 10.586l3.293-3.293a1 1 0 111.414 1.414l-4 4a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 010-1.414z"
                                clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                        </svg>
                    </span>
                </summary>
                <div class="px-6 pb-6">
                    <p class="mt-3 text-secondary">
                        Currently, our focus is on delivering the best possible
                        experience for iOS users. An Android version might be
                        considered in the future based on demand.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </details>

            <details
                class="group bg-card rounded-2xl border border-gray-100 dark:border-gray-800 shadow-lg shadow-black/5 dark:shadow-none transition duration-300 ease-in-out hover:border-brand-accent/50 hover:shadow-brand-glow"
            >
                <summary
                    class="flex justify-between items-center cursor-pointer list-none p-6"
                >
                    <span class="font-medium text-primary"
                        >How can I provide feedback or suggest ideas?</span
                    >
                    <span
                        class="text-secondary group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform duration-200"
                    >
                        <svg
                            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                            class="h-5 w-5"
                            viewBox="0 0 20 20"
                            fill="currentColor"
                            aria-hidden="true"
                        >
                            <path
                                fill-rule="evenodd"
                                d="M5.293 7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0L10 10.586l3.293-3.293a1 1 0 111.414 1.414l-4 4a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 010-1.414z"
                                clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                        </svg>
                    </span>
                </summary>
                <div class="px-6 pb-6">
                    <p class="mt-3 text-secondary">
                        I'd love to hear from you! You can share your thoughts
                        and ideas by replying to the email you receive when you
                        sign up. Once you have access to the beta, you can also
                        give feedback directly through the app.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </details>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
